Package edu.biu.scapi.interactiveMidProtocols.ot

Interface Summary
OTReceiver General interface.
OTRInput Every OT receiver needs inputs during the protocol execution, but every concrete protocol needs different inputs.
OTROutput Every OT receiver outputs a result in the end of the protocol execution, but every concrete protocol output different data.
OTSender General interface.
OTSInput Every OT sender needs inputs during the protocol execution, but every concrete protocol needs different inputs.
OTSMsg Every OT sender should send a message to the receiver, but every concrete protocol sends different data.
 

Class Summary
OTOnByteArrayROutput Concrete implementation of OT receiver (on byteArray) output.
OTOnByteArraySInput Concrete implementation of OT sender (on byteArray) input.
OTOnByteArraySMsg Concrete implementation of OT Privacy sender (on byte array) message.
OTOnGroupElementROutput Concrete implementation of OT receiver (on GroupElement) output.
OTOnGroupElementSInput Concrete implementation of OT sender (on GroupElement) input.
OTOnGroupElementSMsg Concrete implementation of OT Privacy sender (on GroupElement) message.
OTRBasicInput Concrete implementation of OT receiver input.
OTRGroupElementPairMsg Concrete implementation of OT receiver message.
OTRGroupElementQuadMsg Concrete implementation of OT receiver message used by some OT receivers implementations.
OTUtil Utility class used by OT implementations.
OTUtil.RandOutput Holds the output of the above RAND function.
